            "infoHeading": "Blend Details",
            "infoDetails": "<p class=\"scent-name value-sans blue-text mb-1\">Geranium &amp; Ylang Ylang</p>\n<span>Geranium and Ylang Ylang combine with ho wood and clary sage, to transform your home into a tropical paradise.</span>\n\n<p class=\"scent-name value-sans blue-text mb-1 mt-3\">Citronella &amp; Niaouli</p>\n<span class=\"mb-3\">A powerful, fly-repelling blend of citronella java, eucalyptus and peppermint with camphorous niaouli.</span>\n\n<p class=\"scent-name value-sans blue-text mb-1 mt-3\">Linden &amp; Lavender</p>\n<span class=\"mb-3\">A sweet blend of sparkling grapefruit, linden blossom, citrusy neroli and lavender for summer freshness.</span>"
