            "infoHeading": "Blend Details",
            "infoDetails": "<p class=\"scent-name value-sans blue-text mb-1\">Uplifting Citrus</p>\n<span>A fresh and uplifting blend of sweet orange and grapefruit peels with niaouli leaves.</span>\n\n<p class=\"scent-name value-sans blue-text mb-1 mt-3\">Balancing Floral</p>\n<span class=\"mb-3\">A beautifully floral and comforting blend of rose geranium, lemon peel and vetiver roots.</span>\n\n<p class=\"scent-name value-sans blue-text mb-1 mt-3\">Grounding Vetiver</p>\n<span class=\"mb-3\">A complex and earthy blend of sweet orange, coriander seed and vetiver, known for their calming effects.</span>"
